    "text": "Without you, she may lose herself to it."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 111.251,
    "endTime": 113.251,
    "text": "Protect Arendelle at all costs!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 114.126,
    "endTime": 117.625,
    "text": "I believe in you Elsa, more than anyone, or anything."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 128.013,
